{"tid":1965603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[狂賀]驅散悼念8.31群眾男沙展病情轉差入深切治療部插喉","createTime":"2020-04-09T14:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T14:45:24.000Z","uid":44945,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"63a5932861c3c7f125be35d5bfe02bf6a76fd300","tid":1965603,"uid":44945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:44:09.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》製作互動數據圖表合輯 ，分析香港、中國、以至全球疫情百日以來的形勢。<br />\n<br />\n本港3萬名警察，至今4人確診武漢肺炎。上月31日曾在港鐵太子站外驅散悼念8.31群眾的46歲PTU男沙展，是第4位染疫的香港警察，成為本港第854號患者。據悉，該男警病情轉差，有肺衰竭，今日（9日）要入深切治療部插喉。<br />\n<br />\n至於本港的感染個案亦持續遞增，個案接近破千。昨日下午4時至目前新增13宗確診個案，累計確診個案973宗。患者年齡介乎21歲至66歲，5女8男，當中10人有外遊紀錄，包括兩名學生；另有3宗屬本地個案，衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君在記者會指，不能只看單日數字評估趨勢。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fa494ca39616290eec813d210f1c3c855f6203","tid":1965603,"uid":44945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc344fa4eb1b6b3a2018e09b531117da5846c0d3","tid":1965603,"uid":37316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"三萬thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}